OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,FReform-run Kent County Council has
OL,7,Fbeen accused of "fantasy economics"
OL,8,Fafter suggesting they had identified
OL,9,Fmore than #39 million of future budget
OL,10,Fsavings.
OL,12,FThe figure was included in an official
OL,13,Fpress release defending the council's
OL,14,Fwider record on efficiency savings, a
OL,15,Fkey pledge by Nigel Farage's party at
OL,16,Flast year's local elections.
