OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,FBut Labour MP Polly Billington said
OL,7,Fthe claim was "false" because the
OL,8,F#39.5 million was for "unfunded and
OL,9,Funapproved projects" which "had no
OL,10,Fmoney allocated to them".
OL,12,FThe East Thanet MP has spent months
OL,13,Ftrying to obtain details of the
OL,14,Falleged efficiencies from the local
OL,15,Fauthority via freedom of information
OL,16,F(FOI) requests.
