OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,FMs Billington has now written to KCC
OL,7,Fchief executive Amanda Beer. In the
OL,8,Fletter ` seen by ITV News Meridian `
OL,9,Fthe MP writes: "There is nothing to
OL,10,Fsupport the assertion that Reform UK
OL,11,Fhas saved KCC #39.5 million."
OL,13,FThe MP demands "KCC immediately cease
OL,14,Frepeating such claims in official
OL,15,Fcouncil press material", adding: "If
OL,16,Fyou do not do so, I will be left with
OL,17,Fno choice but to escalate the matter".
