OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,FThe original press release, issued on
OL,7,F3 February, said: "KCC is on course to
OL,8,Fdeliver #100 million savings this
OL,9,Fyear, we have reprofiled #39.5 million
OL,10,Fof potential future spend and reduced
OL,11,Fdebt by #67 million."
OL,13,FKent County Council declined our
OL,14,Frequest for an interview.
OL,16,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,17,F"Kent County Council emphatically
OL,18,Frejects these unfounded allegations.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@UO]yD@AOU
