OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,F"We have never claimed #39.5 million
OL,7,Fas savings; our 3 February update
OL,8,Fclearly referred to 'reprofiling
OL,9,Fpotential future spend', not realised
OL,10,Fsavings or approved projects.
OL,12,F"Our FOI responses confirm this. KCC
OL,13,Fhas acted lawfully, impartially and
OL,14,Ftransparently, and we will continue to
OL,15,Fuphold that legal duty, even where
OL,16,Fothers are free to make political
OL,17,Fstatements about the Council."
OL,19,FSpeaking to ITV News Meridian, Polly
OL,20,FBillington disputed KCC's account:
OL,21,F"It's absolutely fantasy economics.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@^O]}D@AOU
