OL,3,CReform-run council accused of 'fantasy
OL,4,Ceconomics' over claimed budget savings
OL,6,F"It's the equivalent of somebody
OL,7,Fcoming into the pub claiming that
OL,8,Fthey're going to buy a really flash
OL,9,Fcar tomorrow and the following day
OL,10,Fsaying that they've saved money by not
OL,11,Fdoing so. If they didn't have the cash
OL,12,Fin the first place, it's not a saving."
OL,14,FKent County Council is due to meet to
OL,15,Fset its budget for the next financial
OL,16,Fyear on Thursday (12 February).
