OL,6,FReform's leader of the council, Cllr
OL,7,FLinden Kemkaran, said in a video
OL,8,Fposted on social media: "We've saved
OL,9,Fmillions, we've reduced the debt and
OL,10,Fwe haven't cut any frontline services."
OL,12,FThe draft budget proposed a council
OL,13,Ftax increase of 3.99%, below the
OL,14,Fmaximum annual 5% rise available to
OL,15,Fmost local authorities.
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat, Tunbridge Wells MP
OL,18,FMike Martin accused the Reform
OL,19,Fadministration at KCC of "quite a lot
OL,20,Fof naivety and quite a lot of
OL,21,Fincompetence".
